race.comment: TERILEE (7) had one run before a short break leading into this, starting favourite at Caulfield Heath and running a solid race under 60kg, perhaps just finding 1200m a touch sharp there. She was promising over the Winter and the stable will have kept her fit for this. PARADISE CITY (1) presents third up having shown good improvement at Flemington when making ground behind a winner who was left alone in front. She can land in a good spot here and take beating. STAGE 'N' SCREEN (2) got the job done last start at Sandown Lakeside to continue a run of good form. She'll be in a good spot again and can figure. SIRIUS STATEMENT (4) is going okay without winning this time in and has minor claims.
